  "body": "User should receive PNs in group chat only in case of replies and mentions. Currently PNs are generated by all types of messages.\r\n\r\n**Preconditions:** User A and User B are members of the same group. User A has enabled notofocations.\r\n\r\n**Steps:** \r\n\r\n1. User B sends regular message in group. \r\n2. See if User A receives PN\r\n\r\n**Actual result:** User A receives PN\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/97245802/0e4b1e38-1b4b-489a-a998-ac05f3976fcc\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n**Expected result:** User A should not receive PN\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly \r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n",
